  "title": "[Fast Hiring!!!] x10 Service Crew- East & Central [Entry Level]",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Summary:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Location: Central/ East</p></li><li><p>Basic + Allowance + Bonus</p></li><li><p>Great career progression</p></li><li><p>Fast hiring! Multiple headcount</p></li><li><p>Company transport</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Responsibility :</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Greet and welcome customers in a warm and professional manner.</p></li><li><p>Present menus, take accurate food and beverage orders, and provide recommendations upon request.</p></li><li><p>Serve food and drinks promptly, ensuring all orders are delivered correctly.</p></li><li><p>Maintain clean, tidy, and properly set-up tables and dining areas before and after service.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with kitchen and bar staff to ensure smooth and efficient service operations.</p></li><li><p>Adhere to hygiene, safety, and service standards at all times.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Key Requirement :</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Candidate with F&B / Service Crew / Waiter / Waitress experience welcome to apply</p></li><li><p>Entry level candidate are welcome to apply as training will be provided</p></li></ul><p><br />To Apply, kindly click on the \"APPLY NOW\" button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Lee Zi Qing (R25126986)</p><p>EA License No: 20C0358</p>",
